    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exemplary specimen featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-pressure VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, ensuring optimal valve timing across the 8,000 RPM range. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight and communicative. Finished in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
