      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously maintained with an open-checkbook policy. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, complemented by pristine alloy wheels that have never seen a curb. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the supple leather seats show no signs of wear, the dashboard remains crack-free, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium surround-sound system to the intuitive navigation\u2014functions flawlessly. It still retains that distinctive new-car scent. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a complete service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new enthusiast behind the wheel.",
